Cap/Black Widow has to deal with a phantom of their past, with the help of an ally from an organization they belonged to previously (Natasha from the avengers in Winter Soldier, Yelena from the widow program in this movie), having a mission assigned by a group behind a conspiracy inhales & conducted by who ends up being the main villain (Robert Redford in TWS, Rachel Weisz here). Not to mention fighting a badass secondary villain that uses a shield and will no doubt become some sort of an ally in the next installment of the franchise (Bucky for the Avengers/Taskmaster for the Thunderbolts).
